prompts.frontCover:
A humorous and vibrant full-body watercolor illustration of a cartoon couple, closely resembling the people in the reference photo. The woman on the left, "Lao Lao," has long, straight dark brown hair, wears gold-rimmed glasses, and a light yellow floral dress with pink flowers. The man on the right, "Jordan," has short, textured dark hair and wears a simple white t-shirt.

They are depicted in a playful, chaotic kitchen scene, joyfully making a birthday feast. Lao Lao is laughing as she expertly folds a dumpling, with a bamboo steamer basket full of them nearby. Jordan, with a slightly panicked but happy expression, is stirring a huge, steaming pot of Chinese porridge (congee) that is threatening to bubble over. In the foreground, a giant, oversized boba tea cup sits between them, filled with milk tea and large tapioca pearls, with two straws in it for them to share. Little splashes of watercolor porridge and a few runaway dumplings are scattered around them on the floor, adding to the fun, messy atmosphere.

The entire scene is rendered in a soft, bright watercolor style with visible paper texture, artistic paint bleeds, and soft edges. The background is a simple, light wash of color to keep the focus on the characters and the food.

In the center of the card, written in a beautiful, flowing handwritten cursive script, is the text: "Happy Birthday, Lao Lao!"

- Reference photos provided for character creation
- Characters should only appear on the front cover
- Transform real people into artistic cartoon/illustrated versions matching the style
- Maintain recognizable features while adapting to the artistic style
